 "pinyin": "lā", "eng": "pull, drag"}, {"ch": "下", "pinyin": "xià", "eng": "under, underneath, below"}, {"ch": "地", "pinyin": "de", "eng": "earth"}, {"ch": "去", "pinyin": "qù", "eng": "go away, leave, depart"}, {"ch": "呢", "pinyin": "ne", "eng": "interrogative or emphatic final"}]}, {"verse": 4, "ref": "Obadiah 1:4", "chinese": "你雖如大鷹高飛，在星宿之間搭窩，我必從那裡拉下你來。這是耶和華說的。", "english": "", "chars": [{"ch": "你", "pinyin": "nǐ", "eng": "you, second person pronoun"}, {"ch": "雖", "pinyin": "suī", "eng": "although, even if"}, {"ch": "如", "pinyin": "rú", "eng": "if, supposing"}, {"ch": "大", "pinyin": "dà", "eng": "big, great, vast, large, high"}, {"ch": "鷹", "pinyin": "yīng", "eng": "eagle, falcon"}, {"ch": "高", "pinyin": "gāo", "eng": "high, tall"}, {"ch": "飛", "pinyin": "fēi", "eng": "fly"}, {"ch": "在", "pinyin": "zài", "eng": "be at, in, on"}, {"ch": "星", "pinyin": "xīng", "eng": "a star, planet"}, {"ch": "宿", "pinyin": "sù", "eng": "stop, rest, lodge, stay overnight"}, {"ch": "之", "pinyin": "zhī", "eng": "marks preceding phrase as modifier of following phrase"}, {"ch": "間", "pinyin": "jiān", "eng": "interval, space"}, {"ch": "搭", "pinyin": "dā", "eng": "join together, attach to"}, {"ch": "窩", "pinyin": "wō", "eng": "nest"}, {"ch": "我", "pinyin": "wǒ", "eng": "our, us, i, me, my, we"}, {"ch": "必", "pinyin": "bì", "eng": "surely, most certainly"}, {"ch": "從", "pinyin": "cóng", "eng": "from, by, since, whence, through"}, {"ch": "那", "pinyin": "nà", "eng": "that, that one, those"}, {"ch": "裡", "pinyin": "lǐ", "eng": "inside, interior, within"}, {"ch": "拉", "pinyin": "lā", "eng": "pull, drag"}, {"ch": "下", "pinyin": "xià", "eng": "under, underneath, below"}, {"ch": "你", "pinyin": "nǐ", "eng": "you, second person pronoun"}, {"ch": "來", "pinyin": "lái", "eng": "come, coming"}, {"ch": "這", "pinyin": "zhè", "eng": "this, the, here"}, {"ch": "是", "pinyin": "shì", "eng": "indeed, yes, right"}, {"ch": "耶", "pinyin": "yé", "eng": "used in transliteration"}, {"ch": "和", "pinyin": "hé", "eng": "harmony, peace"}, {"ch": "華", "pinyin": "huá", "eng": "flowery"}, {"ch": "說", "pinyin": "shuō", "eng": "speak, say, talk"}, {"ch": "的", "pinyin": "de", "eng": "possessive, adjectival suffix"}]}, {"verse": 5, "ref": "Obadiah 1:5", "chinese": "盜賊若來在你那裡，或強盜夜間而來─你何竟被剪除─豈不偷竊直到夠了呢？摘葡萄的若來到你那裡，豈不剩下些葡萄呢？", "english": "", "chars": [{"ch": "盜", "pinyin": "dào", "eng": "rob, steal"}, {"ch": "賊", "pinyin": "zéi", "eng": "thief, traitor"}, {"ch": "若", "pinyin": "ruò", "eng": "if, supposing, assuming"}, {"ch": "來", "pinyin": "lái", "eng": "come, coming"}, {"ch": "在", "pinyin": "zài", "eng": "be at, in, on"}, {"ch": "你", "pinyin": "nǐ", "eng": "you, second person pronoun"}, {"ch": "那", "pinyin": "nà", "eng": "that, that one, those"}, {"ch": "裡", "pinyin": "lǐ", "eng": "inside, interior, within"}, {"ch": "或", "pinyin": "huò", "eng": "or, either, else"}, {"ch": "強", "pinyin": "qiáng", "eng": "strong, powerful, energetic"}, {"ch": "盜", "pinyin": "dào", "eng": "rob, steal"}, {"ch": "夜", "pinyin": "yè", "eng": "night, dark"}, {"ch": "間", "pinyin": "jiān", "eng": "interval, space"}, {"ch": "而", "pinyin": "ér", "eng": "and"}, {"ch": "來", "pinyin": "lái", "eng": "come, coming"}, {"ch": "你", "pinyin": "nǐ", "eng": "you, second person pronoun"}, {"ch": "何", "pinyin": "hé", "eng": "what, why, where, which, how"}, {"ch": "竟", "pinyin": "jìng", "eng": "finally, after all, at last"}, {"ch": "被", "pinyin": "bèi", "eng": "passive indicator 'by'"}, {"ch": "剪", "pinyin": "jiǎn", "eng": "scissors"}, {"ch": "除", "pinyin": "chú", "eng": "eliminate, remove, except"}, {"ch": "豈", "pinyin": "qǐ", "eng": "how? what?"}, {"ch": "不", "pinyin": "bù", "eng": "no, not"}, {"ch": "偷", "pinyin": "tōu", "eng": "to steal, burglar, thief"}, {"ch": "竊", "pinyin": "qiè", "eng": "secretly, stealthily"}, {"ch": "直", "pinyin": "zhí", "eng": "straight, erect, vertical"}, {"ch": "到", "pinyin": "dào", "eng": "go to, arrive, been to"}, {"ch": "夠", "pinyin": "gòu", "eng": "enough, adequate"}, {"ch": "了", "pinyin": "le", "eng